I found a solution... the problem was about the LinearLayoutManager.

the default LinearLayoutManager code that was causing my problem:

    @Override
    public RecyclerView.LayoutParams generateDefaultLayoutParams() {
        return new RecyclerView.LayoutParams(ViewGroup.LayoutParams.WRAP_CONTENT,
                ViewGroup.LayoutParams.WRAP_CONTENT);
    }

the solution that I applied in my fragment:

    bind.contactsRv.layoutManager = object : LinearLayoutManager(this@ContactFragment.context) {
            override fun generateDefaultLayoutParams(): RecyclerView.LayoutParams {
                return RecyclerView.LayoutParams(ViewGroup.LayoutParams.MATCH_PARENT,
                    ViewGroup.LayoutParams.WRAP_CONTENT)
            }
        }

I just override the `ViewGroup.LayoutParams.WRAP_CONTENT` by `ViewGroup.LayoutParams.MATCH_PARENT` in the first parameter of LayoutParams

